==German==
===Etymology===
Hospital slang, because patients are sometimes put on a chair with a hole in the seat when they need to defecate.
===Idiom===
'''Stuhlgang haben'''
# to [[defecate]], or to be able to.
#:''Und Herr Simmtzig, '''hatten''' Sie heute schon '''Stuhlgang'''?''

